1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,040
Si vivís en Valencia,

2
00:00:01,040 --> 00:00:02,080
tenéis que ver esto.

3
00:00:02,080 --> 00:00:02,480
Sobre todo

4
00:00:02,480 --> 00:00:03,360
esta semana.

5
00:00:03,360 --> 00:00:04,000
Petardos,

6
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:04,600
ninots,

7
00:00:04,600 --> 00:00:05,080
fiesta por

8
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:06,080
todas partes...

9
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:06,920
y entre medio,

10
00:00:06,920 --> 00:00:07,800
cosas increíbles

11
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:09,000
tiradas en la acera.

12
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:10,240
Es que la ciudad

13
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:11,080
se llena de tesoros

14
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:11,920
que nadie ve.

15
00:00:11,920 --> 00:00:12,680
La gente limpia,

16
00:00:12,680 --> 00:00:13,080
renueva,

17
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:14,000
cambia muebles...

18
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:14,440
y solo hay

19
00:00:14,440 --> 00:00:15,160
que fijarse.

20
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:16,040
¿Y sabéis qué hago

21
00:00:16,040 --> 00:00:16,600
yo cuando encuentro

22
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:17,280
algo así?

23
00:00:17,280 --> 00:00:18,080
Lo subo a Givore

24
00:00:18,080 --> 00:00:18,840
y en nada

25
00:00:18,840 --> 00:00:19,520
alguien del barrio

26
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:20,360
lo descubre.

27
00:00:20,360 --> 00:00:21,000
Mientras la ciudad

28
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:21,640
celebra,

29
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:22,760
vecinos conectando

30
00:00:22,760 --> 00:00:23,880
sin conocerse.

31
00:00:23,880 --> 00:00:24,480
Segunda vida

32
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:25,400
para todo.

33
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:25,760
Las calles

34
00:00:25,760 --> 00:00:26,400
de Valencia

35
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:27,240
durante Fallas

36
00:00:27,240 --> 00:00:28,360
son una mina.

37
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:29,080
Antes de tirar,

38
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:30,800
pensad si alguien más

39
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:31,840
lo puede aprovechar.

